<refsect1 id="GskStreamListenerSocket.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
This is a <link linkend="GskStreamListener"><type>GskStreamListener</type></link> that takes new input streams
from a raw socket.
</para>
</refsect1>

